    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The Long Cold is an atmospheric ice climbing game set in the present day. Climb out of a crevasse as a group or as a lone climber.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Difficult climbing mechanic using limited controls</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Ice screws acts as checkpoints for the climber</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A deep sprawling level with multiple paths</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Various obstacles while climbing such as loose ice, rock and waterfalls</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A dynamic stamina system while climbing</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Climb solo or in a Group</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The Long Climb can be a solo or group effort of managing stamina, speed and your lifelines (ice screws) which act as checkpoints on your route back to the surface.</p>",
